---
description: "Backend testing requirements"
globs:
  - "backend/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Run `backend/test-preflight.sh` before backend tests.
- Run `backend/test.sh` for backend changes before commit.
- Ensure required env/tooling is present (`python3`, `pytest`, dependencies).
- Integration tests may require service credentials and Redis/Firestore access.
- See AGENTS.md for full rules.
